          </p>
          <h1 class="vcr-font text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold drop-shadow-2xl animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-200" style="color: #508FA3;">
            <span class="inline-block bg-linear-to-r from-[#3A7A8F] via-[#508FA3] to-[#6BA0B3] bg-clip-text text-transparent group-hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
              Elon Woo
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="vcr-font text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg xl:text-xl text-gray-700 drop-shadow-lg animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-400 group-hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors">
